[I] Creats global (system-wide) Compose cache files

[T] Mkcomposecache is used for creating global (system-wide) Compose cache
[T] files.
[T]
[T] Compose cache files help with application startup times and memory usage,
[T] especially in locales with large Compose tables (e.g. all UTF-8 locales).

